snippet.title: "Another Eden: The Cat Beyond Time and Space" Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
#AnotherEden 
The mobile adventure RPG "Another Eden: The Cat Beyond Time and Space" is coming early 2019! Now available on Google Play and the App Store!

Official YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCp0Xenz3Tv-ZTvxlCbPsQ8g

Official Site:https://en.another-eden.jp/

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AnotherEdenRPG.en/

Twitter:https://twitter.com/AnotherEdenRPG

App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1439565347

Google Play:https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=games.wfs.anothereden
